---
title: Tilapia Provençale with Citrus & Herb Veggies
description: Steaming gets a bad rep in the kitchen - but hear us out! Aside from its heart-healthiness, steaming can infuse flavors like no other. In this dish, we're steaming tilapia on a bed of vegetables with aromatics on top. The final product becomes perfumed with lemon and thyme, a classic Provencal pairing.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54ef51b16ced6eb3558b4567.jpg
